title: Kohinoor Cuisine of India
typeOfFood: Lacto, Indian, Buffet, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located one mile from Arizona State, this Indian food place offers a la carte as well as daily lunch and dinner buffet. The appetizers are vegan suitable (samosa, falafel stuffed bread, pakora, etc.), but most sweets contain dairy. Has Indian beers. Vegans to specify.
